---
import "animate.css";
---

<section class="container mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 text-center py-10 md:py-32 text-white">
  <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-tight">
    No client too small.<br />
    No cause too big.
  </h1>

  <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
    With the Ranks works with organizations of all sizes, from the smallest city council races to the largest global non-profits.
  </p>

  <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
    We love building beautiful websites, developing custom organizing tools, running A/B testing programs, hosting Spoke peer-to-peer texting, and doing whatever we can to help good causes prevail.
  </p>

  <p class="text-xl font-medium mb-12">We work with folks like...</p>

  <!-- Scrolling Partner Logos -->
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
    <div class="logo-carousel flex gap-8">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-8 animate-scroll">
        <!-- Only show 3 images at a time -->
        <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Frame%20225-oStGZaKEKe6YCSZxb6Oe7N8mAog0vg.png" alt="350 logo" class="h-32" />
        <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Frame%20226-z3aIFSWzbT9BEnD3cfM8apQPIotV87.png" alt="Indivisible logo" class="h-32" />
        <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Frame%20229-76eAbSPo0nJtrYftESNnCUM5OJFsH2.png" alt="Bernie logo" class="h-32" />
        <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Frame%20228-815CNBvX8XVlzkktQAI9mOsfpULVBZ.png" alt="Power in Numbers logo" class="h-32" />
        <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Frame%20230-UBAndBF14uPgIXhuYeKwr2VlEXcePD.png" alt="American Economic Liberties Project logo" class="h-32" />

        <!-- Duplicate for infinite scroll -->
        <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Frame%20225-oStGZaKEKe6YCSZxb6Oe7N8mAog0vg.png" alt="350 logo" class="h-32" />
        <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Frame%20226-z3aIFSWzbT9BEnD3cfM8apQPIotV87.png" alt="Indivisible logo" class="h-32" />
        <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Frame%20229-76eAbSPo0nJtrYftESNnCUM5OJFsH2.png" alt="Bernie logo" class="h-32" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
    We don't work for Republicans, grifters, corporations, or anyone else afraid to stand up for workers or the planet.
  </p>
</section>

<!-- Full Width Image Section -->
<section class="relative w-full h-[600px] md:h-[980px] bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Group%20238-IBnNqE8rlmH7odjQxKXoh0qur61ThZ.png');">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#252753] via-[#252753]/60 to-transparent -z-50"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 h-full flex flex-col justify-end pb-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start max-w-6xl">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4 text-white text-end">
          Good tech<br />
          for <span class="italic">all.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white">
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          With the Ranks was built by members of the Bernie 2020 technology team to ensure that people working
          on good causes - regardless of their size - could have access to presidential quality tech.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center text-white hover:text-[#8c9dff] transition-colors group">
          <span class="border-b border-current">Learn more about our cooperative</span>
          <span class="ml-2">‚Üù</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .animate-scroll {
    display: flex;
    animation: scroll 15s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes scroll {
    from {
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
    to {
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }
  }
</style>
